{
  "stem": "9245.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, the-- the-- the way the Jews were separate-- situated, they had their own stable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had a cow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is how we had our own milk, butter, cheeses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And vegetables, we had a big-- in our case, we had a huge garden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we planted our own vegetables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The-- the-- the girls, which was myself, my-- my sister, and I, and my brother, we were going to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were also working a little bit in-- in offices.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was an awful laugh-- a lot of time spent standing in line for food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But life was-- naturally, it wasn't a democracy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was communism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was entirely different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But it was bearable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, what-- then, in 1941, when the Second World War started, we-- we had a very-- a-- an outstanding, tremendous assistant by the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They prepared railway cars, trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, to the Jewish population and, for that matter, for to everybody, whoever wants to evacuate and avoid remaining with a German government, you can do so.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, a lot of people did, in our town, those who were connected with the communist regime in a private way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I really begged my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow, I had a premonition that it will not be right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the news trickled down not too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have any radios-- television, for sure not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it trickled down that the situation for the Jews wasn't so good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I approached my father, and I said, look, there's a train here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you can take whatever stuff-- naturally, you have to leave everything, your house, and-- and-- and whatever possessions you have.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's not a life under communism.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
